changes.title: MainMenu
changes.description: Drastically improved performance by optimizing the rendering of the changelog rectangles

changes.title: Inventory
changes.description: Fixed a bug where the rotations from the player in the inventory is not looking at the mouse as it normally does

changes.title: DebugInfo
changes.description: Fixed a bug where even though the player pressed f3 (or the key for debug screen) it wont show the debug screen

changes.title: SmoothCamera
changes.description: Fixed a bug that the smooth camera is not working

changes.title: Slider
changes.description: Fixed an bug where you would get to show values as 0.0002 because the values are not rounded

changes.title: InventoryMove
changes.description: The user can now select between two functionalities: LookAround and FreeMove, they can also be used together, so the user can look around without being able to move, so the feature does not depend on each other

changes.title: MinecraftModifications
changes.description: Added some functionalities to the MinecraftModifications module which allows you to change how the game looks like

changes.title: TargetESP
changes.description: Added Health and Armor indicators to the TargetESP
